title: 10 Cozy Snapchat Lenses for Fall 2020
description: Sweater weather and pumpkin spice? Yes please! The leaves are changing colors and Thanksgiving is just around the corner. Here are 10 cozy Snapchat lenses to help you enjoy autumn with style.
intro: Sweater weather and pumpkin spice? Yes please! The leaves are changing colors and Thanksgiving is just around the corner. Here are 10 cozy Snapchat lenses to help you enjoy autumn with style.

filters.name: Autumn Is Here
filters.author: Danny Marree
filters.description: A nice orange hue, falling fall leaves, what else could you ask for? Our first entry from Danny does a great job at getting you in the fall mood.

filters.name: Pumpkins
filters.author: lexi
filters.description: We might be done carving jack-o-lanterns now that Halloween is done, but pumpkins are still very much a part of fall.

filters.name: Hand Turkey
filters.author: Phil Walton
filters.description: It was a rite of passage when we were younger - tracing your hand and drawing in a turkey. Re-live the glory days with the Hand Turkey lens.

filters.name: Pumpkin Pie Face
filters.author: Jonathan Shoemaker
filters.description: What is Thanksgiving without pumpkin pie? Actually like a normal Thanksgiving, just without the pumpkin pie. But if you must have it, try out this lens by Jonathan.

filters.name: Pumpkin Spice Latte
filters.author: Phil Walton
filters.description: Two lenses from Phil on the same list? What can I say, he makes some good lenses. Nothing says falltime like a pumpkin spice latte, so turn yourself into one!

filters.name: fall vibes
filters.author: natalie suto
filters.description: Sometimes you just need a nice filter to get those fall vibes. If that's you, Natalie's got you covered.

filters.name: Library
filters.author: Karney Li
filters.description: There's nothing like the smell of books and warmth of the library on a chilly day. You can almost smell the books while using this filter.

filters.name: corn
filters.author: amalya <3
filters.description: Corn-on-the-cob is definitely a summertime thing, but by golly if corn isn't great in the falltime too. Show your support for corn with this filter from amalya.

filters.name: Turkey Dinner
filters.author: SoulPancake
filters.description: Look like a Thanksgiving feast with this lens from SoulPancake. Just make sure the Bumpus hounds aren't around, I hear they like turkey...

filters.name: CINNAMON SUGAR
filters.author: Rosa🍁
filters.description: Get some nice warm vibes and sparkles with this filter by Rosa.

filters.name: Bonus - Fall Outfit
filters.author: Snapchat
filters.description: I like to stick to community creators for these lists, but I really liked this lens from Snapchat.
